 theme parks<br>Dislikes: Days without wind<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/62fee427b0f8e2d38be500207d5e4731.poster.avif?t=1725396504\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/62fee427b0f8e2d38be500207d5e4731.webm?t=1725396504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/62fee427b0f8e2d38be500207d5e4731.mp4?t=1725396504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>THE CAT</strong><br>Name: Scott<br>Abillity: Wall Climbing<br>Likes: Climbing on top of fridges<br>Dislikes: Being cuddled too hard<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/20e8be33312d18d709f86a7a347edaad.poster.avif?t=1725396504\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/20e8be33312d18d709f86a7a347edaad.webm?t=1725396504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/20e8be33312d18d709f86a7a347edaad.mp4?t=1725396504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>THE FROG</strong><br>Name: Papo<br>Abillity: Dive Jumping<br>Likes: Trampolines on pools<br>Dislikes: Being mistaken for a toad<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/7a7eca2c58c6b58d1d57e85c9151f673.poster.avif?t=1725396504\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2344060/extras/7a7eca2c58c6b58d1d57e85c9151f673.webm?t=1725396504\" 