rong>Thrilling to complete</strong> - Completionist players will be pleased by a numerous amount of achievements to accomplish in this game!<br></li><li> <strong>It's just so cute!</strong> - Everything, from the colorful levels to the beautifully animated pixel art, will make a cute and fun experience. You're gonna have trouble deciding your favorite character!</li></ul>",
